4
00:00:25,233 --> 00:00:27,901
Make sure that two CCTVs are installed here,

5
00:00:27,902 --> 00:00:30,446
and see to it that Miss Eva
is never alone, alright?

6
00:00:30,447 --> 00:00:31,989
Every step she takes,
every move she makes,

7
00:00:31,990 --> 00:00:35,367
someone should always be with her—
Even when she goes to the restroom.

8
00:00:35,368 --> 00:00:38,287
[GINO] We are the “Gardogs”!

9
00:00:38,288 --> 00:00:40,122
[GINO HOWLS]

10
00:00:40,123 --> 00:00:42,542
[JANA] Miss Eva and Noreen are no longer here...

11
00:00:43,209 --> 00:00:45,628
That’s what the “Room for Rent” sign is for!

12
00:00:49,758 --> 00:00:51,342
[GARDO] People like her
can be very cunning.

13
00:00:51,509 --> 00:00:54,094
So, are you Team Velma?

14
00:00:54,095 --> 00:00:57,556
Or Team Shari - Beauty Reborn?

15
00:00:57,557 --> 00:01:00,893
[VIDEO] #ShariWillWin!

16
00:01:00,894 --> 00:01:03,521
Sir, Noreen has already move out of their house.

17
00:01:04,773 --> 00:01:09,569
Your mission was compromised the moment
you sent me that flash drive.

18
00:01:11,029 --> 00:01:11,988
[NOREEN] Shari.

19
00:01:11,989 --> 00:01:14,574
She has something important to say.

20
00:01:16,618 --> 00:01:20,080
Tell her, Shari.
You promised me.

21
00:01:22,874 --> 00:01:24,751
I think Miss Velma...

22
00:01:25,668 --> 00:01:27,962
Miss Velma killed Helena.

23
00:01:28,546 --> 00:01:35,345
[GANDA GANDAHAN BY DIA MATÉ PLAYING]

24
00:02:14,926 --> 00:02:16,261
Helena...

25
00:02:18,930 --> 00:02:22,475
she was my first friend at
Velma Beauty back then,

26
00:02:24,978 --> 00:02:27,772
and probably the only
friend that I ever had.

27
00:02:31,151 --> 00:02:32,944
The first time that we met,

28
00:02:35,738 --> 00:02:40,118
I was scheduled for a job interview.

29
00:02:41,119 --> 00:02:44,956
But the receptionist refused to let me in because...
[SHARI SNIFFLES]

30
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:52,338
they thought I didn’t belong
at Velma Beauty because I was hideous.

31
00:02:53,047 --> 00:02:56,091
[CORA] Madame Velma wants
to see you in her office!

32
00:02:56,092 --> 00:02:57,342
For real?!

33
00:02:57,343 --> 00:03:00,430
[CORA] Yes! She got the
sample soap you made.

34
00:03:01,222 --> 00:03:03,307
[SHARI EXCLAIMS] Power to Miss Velma!

35
00:03:03,308 --> 00:03:05,267
Your dreams are powerful!

36
00:03:05,268 --> 00:03:07,269
Your dreams are beautiful!

37
00:03:07,270 --> 00:03:09,606
[SHARI CHEERING]
[EVERYONE CHEERING]

38
00:03:10,773 --> 00:03:12,150
[SHARI] She was there.

39
00:03:13,818 --> 00:03:15,236
Helena.
[SHARI SOBS]

40
00:03:21,326 --> 00:03:24,579
She stood up for me to the receptionist.

41
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:29,542
And since then, we became friends.

42
00:03:31,252 --> 00:03:33,087
She even took me under her wing.

43
00:03:34,047 --> 00:03:39,969
Helena was the only person
who encouraged me...[SHARI SOBS]

44
00:03:41,888 --> 00:03:48,019
not to give up every single time
Miss Velma scolded me...[SHARI SOBS]

45
00:03:49,562 --> 00:03:51,898
because my ideas always failed.

46
00:03:53,524 --> 00:03:58,655
She was the only one who
believed that I could do better.

47
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:02,867
She was the only one nice to me.

48
00:04:06,162 --> 00:04:07,956
So why did you betray her?

49
00:04:15,129 --> 00:04:16,589
[SHARI INHALES DEEPLY]

50
00:04:18,633 --> 00:04:20,426
Because I was jealous of her...

51
00:04:22,804 --> 00:04:28,351
because she was always amazing,
and Miss Velma always praised her...

52
00:04:29,602 --> 00:04:31,437
she was always the star.

53
00:04:32,647 --> 00:04:35,650
Also, Miss Velma kept comparing me to her.

54
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:44,367
It's a good thing you finally came clean.

55
00:04:50,832 --> 00:04:53,375
For someone who grew
up without any friends...

56
00:04:53,376 --> 00:04:54,502
[SHARI SOBS]

57
00:04:57,088 --> 00:04:59,841
I didn't know how to be one.
[SHARI SOBS]

58
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:05,555
[SHARI SOBS]

59
00:05:07,515 --> 00:05:10,268
But I still
didn't stop being her friend.

60
00:05:13,730 --> 00:05:16,232
I even celebrated her achievements alongside her.

61
00:05:16,983 --> 00:05:17,734
[SHARI SNIFFLES]

62
00:05:19,527 --> 00:05:21,029
Take it easy.

63
00:05:22,989 --> 00:05:24,157
- Shari?
- Hmm?

64
00:05:24,699 --> 00:05:26,117
Let's go home?

65
00:05:28,953 --> 00:05:29,746
Sorry...

66
00:05:29,747 --> 00:05:30,830
I’m sorry.

67
00:05:32,707 --> 00:05:33,916
Uh... I’m sorry.

68
00:05:35,501 --> 00:05:40,672
Honestly, if Shari hadn’t pushed me
to join you, I wouldn’t have...

69
00:05:40,673 --> 00:05:41,841
Because it’s embarrassing.

70
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:43,718
Why’s that?

71
00:05:45,011 --> 00:05:50,224
[EDDIE SCOFFS] I’m the chairman of the company
that is in charge of Velma Beauty, right?

72
00:05:50,433 --> 00:05:52,727
That basically makes us coworkers.

73
00:05:53,561 --> 00:05:55,813
Mmm, not really.

74
00:05:56,481 --> 00:05:57,815
[HELENA] You’re my boss.

75
00:05:58,608 --> 00:06:00,568
You’re Miss Velma’s husband.

76
00:06:01,277 --> 00:06:04,280
We never thought we’d actually
get to bond with you.

77
00:06:04,614 --> 00:06:05,615
Which is nice, right?

78
00:06:06,366 --> 00:06:07,075
Cheers.

79
00:06:07,867 --> 00:06:08,534
Cheers.

80
00:06:08,535 --> 00:06:09,619
[GLASSES CLINKING]

81
00:06:17,377 --> 00:06:18,419
Shari?

82
00:06:18,961 --> 00:06:20,046
Just please let me know, alright?

83
00:06:20,588 --> 00:06:21,381
[SHARI MUMBLES]

84
00:06:22,090 --> 00:06:23,049
Is she fine?

85
00:06:27,303 --> 00:06:28,303
You're so nice, sir.

86
00:06:28,304 --> 00:06:29,389
Thank you.

87
00:06:30,598 --> 00:06:32,475
Miss Velma is lucky to have you.

88
00:06:32,642 --> 00:06:35,978
You know how to get along with everyone,
and you're down-to-earth.

89
00:06:36,979 --> 00:06:38,564
You act as if you're not an Imperial.

90
00:06:38,981 --> 00:06:39,816
[HELENA LAUGHS AWKWARDLY]

91
00:06:40,024 --> 00:06:41,150
I'm glad you feel that way.

92
00:06:42,276 --> 00:06:43,902
And I will drink to that.

93
00:06:43,903 --> 00:06:44,487
[HELENA LAUGHS LIGHTLY]

94
00:06:44,488 --> 00:06:47,323
[EDDIE CHUCKLES LIGHTLY]

95
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:49,700
Mmm.

96
00:06:50,910 --> 00:06:51,661
Are you okay? Let me help you.

97
00:06:51,661 --> 00:06:52,453
This is embarrassing.

98
00:06:55,289 --> 00:06:56,374
Uh... it's fine.

99
00:06:56,707 --> 00:06:57,791
I'll handle it, sir.

100
00:06:57,792 --> 00:06:58,668
I'm sorry.

101
00:06:59,585 --> 00:07:00,503
"Sir?"

102
00:07:01,671 --> 00:07:02,964
You're too formal.

103
00:07:03,506 --> 00:07:06,133
I mean at the office, yes, I'm an Imperial.

104
00:07:06,134 --> 00:07:10,680
But outside, I'm just Eddie.

105
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,934
Okay. Sorry.

106
00:07:15,476 --> 00:07:17,478
Um, excuse me,
I'll just go to the restroom.

107
00:07:19,564 --> 00:07:22,358
Shari, I'll just go to the restroom,
and then we'll be leaving.

108
00:07:22,608 --> 00:07:24,193
[EDDIE INHALES DEEPLY]

109
00:07:31,534 --> 00:07:32,493
Shari, you okay?

110
00:07:33,619 --> 00:07:34,620
Shari?

111
00:07:39,917 --> 00:07:40,751
Shari!

112
00:07:48,217 --> 00:07:49,177
[EDDIE SIGHS SHARPLY]

113
00:07:56,517 --> 00:08:00,188
[EDDIE POURING POWDER]

114
00:08:02,899 --> 00:08:05,735
[EDDIE STIRS]

115
00:08:09,238 --> 00:08:12,408
[EDDIE STIRS]

116
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,043
[EDDIE POURS LIQUOR]

117
00:08:33,471 --> 00:08:34,138
You okay?

118
00:08:34,138 --> 00:08:35,097
[HELENA] Yeah.

119
00:08:35,431 --> 00:08:37,266
Shari, let's go.

120
00:08:37,517 --> 00:08:39,392
I've booked us a ride, we're leaving.

121
00:08:39,393 --> 00:08:40,894
[SHARI MUMBLES] Uh... no, no.

122
00:08:40,895 --> 00:08:42,021
Shari.

123
00:08:42,146 --> 00:08:43,731
[SHARI MUMBLES]

124
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,690
Shari, that’s enough.

125
00:08:45,691 --> 00:08:47,401
We still have to go to work tomorrow.

126
00:08:52,073 --> 00:08:53,323
[SHARI GRUNTS]
Let's go home.

127
00:08:53,324 --> 00:08:54,158
[SHARI GROANS]

128
00:08:54,825 --> 00:08:56,452
Sir, we’ll go ahead.

129
00:08:56,953 --> 00:08:58,538
We still have work tomorrow.

130
00:08:58,996 --> 00:09:00,330
My driver is right outside.

131
00:09:00,331 --> 00:09:01,332
I can have him take you home.

132
00:09:01,624 --> 00:09:03,917
Uh... really?

133
00:09:03,918 --> 00:09:04,877
It would be safer.

134
00:09:06,337 --> 00:09:07,337
Are you sure?

135
00:09:07,338 --> 00:09:08,421
Not a problem.

136
00:09:08,422 --> 00:09:09,382
I'll just finish this.

137
00:09:09,383 --> 00:09:11,008
Besides, you're celebrating, right?

138
00:09:11,384 --> 00:09:11,968
So...

139
00:09:13,844 --> 00:09:14,637
Cheers!

140
00:09:16,514 --> 00:09:17,847
- Cheers.
- [EDDIE] Congratulations.

141
00:09:17,848 --> 00:09:18,724
[GLASSES CLINKING]

142
00:09:18,725 --> 00:09:20,226
Thank you.
[HELENA SCOFFS AWKWARDLY]

143
00:09:50,214 --> 00:09:51,257
Shari?

144
00:09:51,924 --> 00:09:52,508
Shari?

145
00:09:52,508 --> 00:09:53,301
Oh my, let's go.

146
00:09:53,302 --> 00:09:54,760
Come on. Let's go.

147
00:09:55,011 --> 00:09:56,762
[SHARI MUMBLES]

148
00:09:58,222 --> 00:09:58,931
Shari?

149
00:10:00,474 --> 00:10:01,392
Shari?

150
00:10:05,938 --> 00:10:07,023
- Uh, sir...
- [EDDIE] What's up?

151
00:10:07,398 --> 00:10:08,899
- Is she okay?
- [HELENA] Shari...

152
00:10:11,319 --> 00:10:12,445
[EDDIE] Hey, how about you?

153
00:10:13,904 --> 00:10:15,239
[EDDIE] Are you okay?
[HELENA GRUNTS LIGHTLY]

154
00:10:43,017 --> 00:10:44,517
But I was too late...

155
00:10:44,518 --> 00:10:45,436
[SHARI SOBS]

156
00:10:48,731 --> 00:10:50,190
then I was too drunk.

157
00:10:50,191 --> 00:10:51,025
[SHARI SOBS] I...

158
00:10:54,987 --> 00:10:55,613
[SHARI SOBS]

159
00:10:59,659 --> 00:11:06,457
I didn't know what to do,
but deep inside, Noreen...

160
00:11:07,667 --> 00:11:09,085
Noreen, I knew, [SHARI SOBS]

161
00:11:10,044 --> 00:11:12,672
I knew that something
bad had happened.

162
00:11:15,508 --> 00:11:17,218
And you did nothing?

163
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:25,393
[SHARI SNIFFLES] Noreen, I tried.

164
00:11:26,185 --> 00:11:27,227
I tried.
[SHARI SOBS]

165
00:11:27,228 --> 00:11:28,979
I talked to Sir Eddie.

166
00:11:30,815 --> 00:11:31,732
Sir Eddie.

167
00:11:32,441 --> 00:11:33,359
[EDDIE] Shari?

168
00:11:36,278 --> 00:11:37,862
Can I talk to you?

169
00:11:37,863 --> 00:11:39,240
Yeah, anything.

170
00:11:40,408 --> 00:11:42,743
It's about what happened last night.

171
00:11:43,536 --> 00:11:44,286
Wasn't it fun?

172
00:11:44,287 --> 00:11:45,287
I had fun.

173
00:11:45,288 --> 00:11:47,455
I hope you enjoyed because judging
by your face, it seems like...

174
00:11:47,456 --> 00:11:48,791
I saw what you did.

175
00:11:49,667 --> 00:11:51,836
You put something in Helena's drink.

176
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:00,428
And...

177
00:12:02,471 --> 00:12:04,931
you left as if Helena was unconscious.

178
00:12:04,932 --> 00:12:06,016
Stop.

179
00:12:07,810 --> 00:12:10,020
Okay, I don't know
where you're getting this.

180
00:12:11,939 --> 00:12:14,275
I didn't put anything in Helena's drink.

181
00:12:16,026 --> 00:12:17,653
You were so wasted.

182
00:12:19,196 --> 00:12:21,699
I'd be surprised if you
actually saw anything at all.

183
00:12:22,616 --> 00:12:23,409
You're mistaken.

184
00:12:23,410 --> 00:12:24,994
I’m certain I saw something.

185
00:12:25,244 --> 00:12:27,830
[EDDIE EXHALES SHARPLY]

186
00:12:28,330 --> 00:12:29,539
[SHARI SOBS LIGHTLY]

187
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:32,418
I saw you carrying
Helena on the way out.

188
00:12:35,838 --> 00:12:36,797
Yes, Shari.

189
00:12:36,798 --> 00:12:39,215
Helena and I, we went home together.

190
00:12:39,216 --> 00:12:40,759
We left together.

191
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:41,927
What is... [EDDIE SIGHS]

192
00:12:44,764 --> 00:12:47,516
Whatever it is you're insinuating
here, I don't appreciate it.

193
00:12:48,392 --> 00:12:49,101
Listen,

194
00:12:49,894 --> 00:12:50,935
Helena is an adult.

195
00:12:50,936 --> 00:12:52,187
She is a grown woman.

196
00:12:52,188 --> 00:12:53,898
She knows what she got herself into.

197
00:12:55,357 --> 00:12:57,318
[EDDIE] She knows what she wants.

198
00:12:58,903 --> 00:13:00,154
I just gave it to her.

199
00:13:05,743 --> 00:13:08,161
And you did it behind Miss Velma's back?

200
00:13:08,162 --> 00:13:10,663
Helena did what she did
to get on my good side.

201
00:13:10,664 --> 00:13:12,166
What is this about?

202
00:13:14,502 --> 00:13:15,377
Wait a minute.

203
00:13:18,088 --> 00:13:19,173
Is that what this is?

204
00:13:22,843 --> 00:13:24,470
Are you trying to get on my good side?

205
00:13:36,565 --> 00:13:39,693
[EDDIE] Everything I gave
Helena, I can give to you as well.

206
00:13:43,364 --> 00:13:45,115
I am teasing, come on.

207
00:13:45,533 --> 00:13:51,580
But seriously, whatever it is you need,
you can call me, anytime, okay?

208
00:13:54,124 --> 00:13:56,627
[EDDIE INHALES DEEPLY]
One more thing...

209
00:13:56,919 --> 00:14:01,382
I really don't appreciate you slinging
around these serious accusations.

210
00:14:03,384 --> 00:14:08,013
It could seriously damage your reputation, and hurt your career.

211
00:14:09,807 --> 00:14:10,808
We don't want that.

212
00:14:12,518 --> 00:14:13,811
I suggest you drop it.

213
00:14:14,228 --> 00:14:15,396
There's no story here.

214
00:14:19,275 --> 00:14:27,366
[SHARI SIGHS ANXIOUSLY]

215
00:14:32,162 --> 00:14:33,789
[SHARI] Are you sure, Helena?

216
00:14:36,208 --> 00:14:39,336
Sir Eddie did this to me, Shari.

217
00:14:43,549 --> 00:14:44,757
Helena, of all people,

218
00:14:44,758 --> 00:14:47,428
do you really think Sir Eddie could have
done something terrible to you?

219
00:14:49,054 --> 00:14:50,848
He’s not someone you’d want to mess with!

220
00:14:51,223 --> 00:14:54,726
Helena... you might regret making such an accusation!

221
00:14:54,727 --> 00:14:57,396
Shari, I’m being honest with you.

222
00:14:59,523 --> 00:15:00,858
Are you really sure?

223
00:15:03,277 --> 00:15:07,071
Maybe you were the one who went to him,

224
00:15:07,072 --> 00:15:09,616
tempted him, and made him think it was okay.

225
00:15:09,617 --> 00:15:11,201
Shari, I’m not like that!

226
00:15:12,161 --> 00:15:13,244
That’s why I told you...

227
00:15:13,245 --> 00:15:15,413
I thought you’d understand me first.

228
00:15:15,414 --> 00:15:16,957
You know what I understand?

229
00:15:17,374 --> 00:15:19,668
I get that you have dreams,

230
00:15:20,628 --> 00:15:22,755
and that’s why you went
after Sir Eddie, right?

231
00:15:23,797 --> 00:15:25,132
Alright, let me guess...
[HELENA SCOFFS]

232
00:15:25,424 --> 00:15:27,675
If he didn’t choose you, you’d probably
end up blackmailing him.

233
00:15:27,676 --> 00:15:28,676
Shari!

234
00:15:28,677 --> 00:15:29,761
Just admit it, Helena!

235
00:15:29,762 --> 00:15:30,763
Just come clean!

236
00:15:31,305 --> 00:15:33,349
Just admit that you like Sir Eddie.

237
00:15:34,099 --> 00:15:37,018
Also, you probably thought that
if you show him how you felt,

238
00:15:37,019 --> 00:15:38,187
he might love you back.

239
00:15:38,562 --> 00:15:39,646
And maybe... just maybe,

240
00:15:39,647 --> 00:15:41,273
you want to take Miss Velma’s place!

241
00:15:41,732 --> 00:15:42,566
Shari!

242
00:15:42,567 --> 00:15:44,567
You just want to be the one
calling all the shots here!

243
00:15:44,568 --> 00:15:45,610
[HELENA] Shari... hear me out!

244
00:15:45,611 --> 00:15:46,320
Please help me!

245
00:15:46,321 --> 00:15:47,987
You're so delusional, and you're a snake too!

246
00:15:47,988 --> 00:15:50,073
Shari, please, help me!

247
00:15:50,074 --> 00:15:50,824
Shari!

248
00:15:50,825 --> 00:15:52,242
What do you want?!

249
00:15:54,411 --> 00:15:55,788
For me to betray Sir Eddie?!

250
00:15:57,539 --> 00:15:59,750
That's not gonna happen, Helena!

251
00:16:00,042 --> 00:16:01,418
[HELENA SOBS] Please...

252
00:16:01,669 --> 00:16:03,128
This is all your fault!

253
00:16:06,715 --> 00:16:08,342
[HELENA SIGHS NERVOUSLY] Shari...

254
00:16:08,968 --> 00:16:09,802
Shari...

255
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:14,306
[SHARI SIGHS IN DISTRESS]

256
00:16:21,397 --> 00:16:22,815
Shari...

257
00:16:24,024 --> 00:16:25,566
Helena, can you please stop?!

258
00:16:25,567 --> 00:16:26,485
Leave me alone!

259
00:16:26,735 --> 00:16:29,279
Shari, please believe me.

260
00:16:31,490 --> 00:16:33,993
[SHARI SIGHS IN DISTRESS] Fine.

261
00:16:34,868 --> 00:16:35,536
Whatever.

262
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:42,418
But Helena, you always seemed
happy with Sir Eddie, right?

263
00:16:44,545 --> 00:16:46,630
Shari, do you even realize
what you’re saying?

264
00:16:48,090 --> 00:16:51,969
Just because he was kind to me doesn’t mean
he had the right to take advantage of me!

265
00:16:52,302 --> 00:16:55,472
Helena... how could he not go after you?!

266
00:16:55,806 --> 00:16:58,642
You practically put him on a pedestal that night!

267
00:16:59,935 --> 00:17:03,105
And honestly, how am I supposed
to believe you didn’t want it?

268
00:17:03,605 --> 00:17:05,106
Shari, I was raped!

269
00:17:05,107 --> 00:17:06,524
Why are you making it look like it's my fault?!

270
00:17:06,525 --> 00:17:07,735
Because you're careless!

271
00:17:11,989 --> 00:17:15,324
It's not my fault that you tempted Sir Eddie.

272
00:17:15,325 --> 00:17:17,619
And it's also not my fault
you were being a flirt!

273
00:17:18,162 --> 00:17:19,246
[HELENA SLAPS SHARI]
[SHARI GASPS]

274
00:17:22,791 --> 00:17:25,753
[HELENA SOBS] I came to you because
I believed you were my friend, Shari.

275
00:17:27,212 --> 00:17:30,424
I thought you’d understand
what I went through.

276
00:17:32,092 --> 00:17:35,304
But instead, you’ve only made my pain worse.

277
00:17:37,097 --> 00:17:39,141
I don’t know what’s worse, Shari...

278
00:17:39,558 --> 00:17:40,641
The abuse I suffered,

279
00:17:40,642 --> 00:17:44,646
or the fact that my friend
won’t even listen to me.

280
00:18:00,245 --> 00:18:02,413
Miss Velma, please believe me.

281
00:18:02,414 --> 00:18:04,207
I'm telling you the truth.

282
00:18:04,208 --> 00:18:06,167
Sir Eddie raped me.

283
00:18:06,168 --> 00:18:09,213
I'm sure you were the
first to seduce my husband!

284
00:18:09,505 --> 00:18:12,508
And now that you've been caught,
you want to ruin him?!

285
00:18:12,758 --> 00:18:14,592
[HELENA SOBS]
Miss Velma, please... please.

286
00:18:14,593 --> 00:18:17,012
[HELENA GASPS AND GRUNTS]

287
00:18:19,431 --> 00:18:20,849
Find your way out!

288
00:18:23,769 --> 00:18:32,945
[HELENA PANTS]

289
00:18:44,957 --> 00:18:46,166
[SHARI INHALES DEEPLY]

290
00:18:47,459 --> 00:18:49,336
Miss... Miss V.

291
00:18:51,588 --> 00:18:54,423
What if Helena is telling the truth?

292
00:18:54,424 --> 00:18:56,093
[SHARI] What if...

293
00:18:57,302 --> 00:18:58,637
How about this?

294
00:18:58,804 --> 00:18:59,555
Here.

295
00:19:00,222 --> 00:19:04,101
[VELMA] Isn't it obvious that
my husband had an affair with this woman?!

296
00:19:05,394 --> 00:19:10,065
And I'm sure she looked for a
way to make Eddie fall into her trap.

297
00:19:11,900 --> 00:19:13,442
[SHARI SIGHS ANXIOUSLY] But Miss V...

298
00:19:13,443 --> 00:19:16,989
Do you honestly believe her lies?!

299
00:19:18,198 --> 00:19:19,700
[VELMA SIGHS IN DISAPPOINTMENT]

300
00:19:20,534 --> 00:19:24,454
I’m the one being cheated on
by two people whom I trusted!

301
00:19:26,039 --> 00:19:31,503
And you know, this wouldn’t even
be happening if not because of you.

302
00:19:33,255 --> 00:19:36,091
Miss V, how did I get dragged into this?

303
00:19:37,509 --> 00:19:42,389
Because I told Helena that you are
going to be my successor one day.

304
00:19:42,598 --> 00:19:44,558
So there, she got pissed!

305
00:19:48,353 --> 00:19:49,021
[SHARI STAMMERS]

306
00:19:49,022 --> 00:19:53,192
Me? Your successor?

307
00:19:54,193 --> 00:19:55,736
Who else?

308
00:19:56,195 --> 00:19:57,738
You’re the only one who’s truly great.

309
00:19:58,447 --> 00:20:02,034
You’re the only one who can replace Helena—
No one else.

310
00:20:03,118 --> 00:20:05,787
That’s why she got jealous and furious.

311
00:20:06,705 --> 00:20:08,457
[VELMA] That also explains
why she’s doing all of this.

312
00:20:09,791 --> 00:20:13,420
So, Shari, side with me.

313
00:20:14,338 --> 00:20:17,966
Help me fight Helena and all her lies.

314
00:20:20,969 --> 00:20:23,430
I’ll make all your dreams come true.

315
00:20:25,557 --> 00:20:28,185
And I will treat you like my own daughter.

316
00:20:33,565 --> 00:20:35,984
[SHARI SOBS LIGHTLY]

317
00:20:46,912 --> 00:20:47,746
[SHARI SIGHS SHARPLY]

318
00:20:56,588 --> 00:20:57,506
[SHARI SOBS LIGHTLY]

319
00:20:59,758 --> 00:21:01,927
I know that you could be something.

320
00:21:04,388 --> 00:21:05,639
I trust you.

321
00:21:07,641 --> 00:21:14,439
I know you will help me protect
Eddie against all of the lies of Helena.

322
00:21:17,109 --> 00:21:17,609
[SHARI SNIFFLES]

323
00:21:20,028 --> 00:21:22,197
And to prove I intend to
keep my promise to you...

324
00:21:31,873 --> 00:21:33,250
This is yours.

325
00:21:38,839 --> 00:21:42,884
Use it for your brand, Pantasya Beauty.

326
00:21:44,511 --> 00:21:46,471
Isn't this your dream?

327
00:21:57,149 --> 00:21:58,400
[SHARI SIGHS ANXIOUSLY]

328
00:22:05,157 --> 00:22:11,413
When Helena discovered the
truth, she confronted me.

329
00:22:13,623 --> 00:22:15,666
But instead of being honest...

330
00:22:15,667 --> 00:22:17,502
You told her to kill herself.

331
00:22:19,921 --> 00:22:20,756
[SHARI GASPS]

332
00:22:22,758 --> 00:22:26,136
[EDDIE] According to the police,
whoever Marie Armani is...

333
00:22:26,470 --> 00:22:28,513
their prime suspect is Shari.

334
00:22:29,890 --> 00:22:30,974
She’s going to jail.

335
00:22:33,226 --> 00:22:36,104
Thank you, Alex, for your help.

336
00:22:45,655 --> 00:22:48,408
It’s painful to hear the truth from others...

337
00:22:50,202 --> 00:22:56,248
[NOREEN] every detail of
how they treated my sister so cruelly.

338
00:22:56,249 --> 00:22:58,335
[NOREEN CRYING]

339
00:23:01,296 --> 00:23:06,760
[NOREEN CRYING]

340
00:23:06,843 --> 00:23:10,931
I was forced to sign an affidavit,
prepared by Miss Velma,

341
00:23:11,390 --> 00:23:15,102
promising I wouldn’t testify
about what happened.

342
00:23:15,310 --> 00:23:19,523
You turned your back on
Helena because you’re selfish!

343
00:23:21,650 --> 00:23:25,237
Because you’re so
extremely greedy!

344
00:23:25,362 --> 00:23:29,241
I will do anything.
I’ll do anything, Noreen.

345
00:23:29,950 --> 00:23:31,951
I know I can’t bring your sister back,

346
00:23:31,952 --> 00:23:34,746
but I promise to do whatever
it takes to make things right.

347
00:23:35,580 --> 00:23:37,999
Confess everything.

348
00:23:38,875 --> 00:23:40,961
I am Shari de Jesus,

349
00:23:44,214 --> 00:23:46,383
and I admit...
